<lyrics>[V1]
 Ka Jesuh kan dawt ko, Ka Bawipa na si, Nangmah thawngin sual duhnak
 phunkip ka hlawt, A ka Khamhtu le Tlantu Bawipa na si, Hmasa kan dawtnak
 in atu kan dawt deuh.

[V2]
 Na ka dawt hmasa ca, Nangmah kha kan dawt, Keimah sual thlahnak ca,
 Vailam thah na in, Hling luchin naa chinh ca nangmah kan dawt chin, Hmasa
 kan dawtnak in atu kan dawt deuh.

[V3]
 Ka nun siseh, ka thih siseh kan dawt lai, Ka nunnak um chung vialte
 kan thangthat lai, Ka cah lai caan hmanh ah hi bang ka chim lai, Hmasa
 kan dawtnak in atu kan dawt deuh.

[V4]
 A zungzal in timh cia lawmhnak innchung ah, Kan in biak ngai te lai,
 Pathian vancung ah, Sunpar luchin chinh in hi hla ka sa lai, Hmasa kan
 dawt nakin atu kan dawt deuh.</lyrics>
<key>F</key>
<title>JESUH, KAN DAWT CH344</title>
</song>